cdata.name: iXledger
cdata.desc: InsureX is a decentralized marketplace for insurance products based on blockchain technology. This alternative marketplace aims to bringinsurers, reinsurers and brokers together in an efficient, cost-effective and transparent manner that skips middlemen and unneeded fees. The InsureX (IXT) token is the underlying token used in the InsureX market bythecommunity, customers andpartners to buy data and premium services.
